    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_8419504271689793415.png",
                "id": "talent38067",
                "key": "蠍爪鉗擊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "蠍爪鉗擊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p>生成1張<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">噬骸能量塊</span>，隨機置入我方牌庫頂部2張卡牌之中。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/86ad2f9a487b5e1fc7f14c6d3aebf17a_5163084852052078959.png",
                "id": "talent7222",
                "key": "蠍尾錐刺",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "蠍尾錐刺"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span>手牌中最多3張<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">噬骸能量塊</span>，在對方場上生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷錐陷阱</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷錐陷阱</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所在陣營的角色使用技能後：</span>對所在陣營的出戰角色造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：</span>初始為建立時所棄置的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">噬骸能量塊</span>張數。（最多疊加到3）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/aebba01f5c8d920339645f679cd512aa_4999544917522289568.png",
                "id": "talent64663",
                "key": "雷錐散射",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷錐散射"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】回合結束時，生成2張<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">噬骸能量塊</span>，隨機置入我方牌庫頂部10張卡牌之中。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/2f5fbc2acab943dc5e598980c758f964_6280095560220086256.png",
                "id": "talent45052",
                "key": "不朽亡骸‧雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "不朽亡骸‧雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">事件牌</span></p><p>隨機<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span>1張原本元素骰費用最高的手牌，生成1個我方出戰角色類型的元素骰。（每回合最多打出1張）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_254642361481936235.png",
                "id": "talent34639",
                "key": "噬骸能量塊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/531ed6322b0a8f721e6080da7fcd72ce_6024861274468479595.png",
                "title": "噬骸能量塊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_8232073347790368758.png",
                "id": "talent74238",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span></p><p>透過行動牌或角色技能的效果，將行動牌從手牌或牌庫中棄置。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4836527869373395641.png",
